'''Accra Inter Allies''' is a [[Ghanaian]] professional [[football team]] that plays in the 3A Zone of the [[Ghana Football Leagues|Ghana Division One League]].<ref name="piojiojoo">{{cite web | url=http://www.ghanafa.org/pages/divisiononeleague/ | title=Division One League | publisher=ghanafa.org | accessdate=19 August 2013 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812201746/http://www.ghanafa.org/pages/divisiononeleague/ | archive-date=2013-08-12 | dead-url=yes | df= }}</ref> Zone 3A has seven competing teams from the part of the [[Greater Accra Region]] and the [[Volta Region]] of Ghana.<ref name="piojiojoo"/>
