'''''Brno Noppeisen''''' was a bilingual workers newspaper issued in [[Brno]] in the 1870s. ''Brno Noppeisen'' was published jointly by [[German people|German]] and [[Czech people|Czech]] socialists in the city.<ref>Institute of Marxism-Leninism of the CPCz CC, Institute of Marxism-Leninism of the CPS CC. ''An Outline of the History of the CPCz''. [[Prague]]: Orbis Press Agency, 1980. p. 25</ref>
