{{Infobox musical artist | name = Kadiatou Holm Keita | image = kadiatou.jpg | caption = Kadiatou in 2018 | background = solo_singer | birth_name = Kadiatou Claudine Holm Keita | alias = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|2001|9|6|df=yes}} | death_date = | birth_place = [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]] | origin = [[Uganda]], [[Guinea]] | instrument = | genre = [[Soul music|Soul]], [[R&B]] | occupation = [[Singing|Singer]] | years_active = 2017&ndash;present | label = | associated_acts = | website = | current_members = | past_members = }}
'''Kadiatou Claudine Holm Keita''', (born 6 September 2001) is a Swedish singer.<ref name="mitti.se">{{cite web|url=https://mitti.se/nyheter/kadiatou-larsberg-nasta|title=Kadiatou från Larsberg kan bli nästa Idol|publisher=mitti.se|accessdate=3 December 2018}}</ref> She is of Ugandian and Guinean heritage from her fathers side.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://modette.se/livsstil/915872-allt-du-maste-veta-om-kadiatou-holm-keita-fran-idol-2018|title=Allt du måste veta om Kadiatou Holm Keita från Idol 2018|date=9 October 2018|publisher=modette.se|accessdate=3 December 2018}}</ref> She grew up in [[Lidingö]].<ref name="mitti.se"/>
She is one of the finalists in [[Idol 2018]] which is broadcast on [[TV4 (Sweden)|TV4]].<ref name="tv4.se">{{cite web|url=https://www.tv4.se/idol/artiklar/kadiatou-holm-keita-och-sebastian-wallden-finalister-i-idol-2018-5c01178824bc62f483003097|title=Kadiatou Holm Keita och Sebastian Walldén finalister i Idol 2018 - Idol - tv4.se|publisher=tv4.se|accessdate=3 December 2018}}</ref> She will head up with [[Sebastian Walldén]] in [[Globen]] on 7 December.<ref name="tv4.se"/>
